	&bull; Bachelor&rsquo;s degree<br />
	&bull; 4+ years of marketing/sales, business development, or tech agency experience<br />
	&bull; Strong organizational skills and ability to manage complex processes<br />
	&bull; Proficiency in PowerPoint (design skills are a plus)<br />
	&bull; Strong writing and grammar skills; previous experience with drafting proposals ideal<br />
	&bull; Excellent time-management and multi-tasking skills<br />
	&bull; Knowledge and interest in the technology and start-up industry<br />
	&bull; Strong interpersonal and communication skills<br />
	&bull; Interest in a long-term career and increased responsibilities<br />
