<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">The Senior Account Executive will be a dedicated team working directly with LaunchSquad&rsquo;s managing partners and contributing to the day-to-day activity of teams across multiple accounts. Responsibilities include, but are not limited to: media relations, research, writing, client relations, social media and strategy. Our ideal candidate has solid client services and media-relations experience, and exhibits an independent, creative streak and a whatever-it-takes attitude with clients and teams.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family: Arial;">LaunchSquad offers a fast-paced, fun and rewarding work environment. We&rsquo;re a high-energy, creative, nimble and collegial group who thrives on working with amazing clients and telling change-the-world stories. Our client base includes consumer and business-focused clients across a range of industries, including consumer Internet, entertainment, business software, IT infrastructure, green technology, and mobile.</span></p>
